							<div class="post">&quot;Analog buttons&quot;? &nbsp;I assume by that you mean pushbuttons?<br />74HC165, parallel_in-serial_out shift register, &quot;daisy-chain&quot; two, each switch to &#039;165 input; constantly read the shift register data.<br /><br />Here&#039;s a link to someone who &quot;got it&quot; - <a href="http://arduino.cc/forum/index.php/topic,10069.0.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://arduino.cc/forum/index.php/topic,10069.0.html</a></div>
