									<div class="postSubject" id="subject_600603">
										<a href="http://forum.arduino.cc/index.php?topic=79466.msg600603#msg600603">Re: which controller can i use to connect 15 buttons</a>
									</div>
									<div class="postDate">&#171; <b>Reply #7 on:</b> November 18, 2011, 09:06:46 pm &#187;</div></td>
								<td align="right" valign="bottom" height="20" class="postIconMenu">	
			<a href="#" class="increaseFont"> <img src="http://forum.arduino.cc/Themes/arduinoWide/images/buttons/edit-size-up.png" alt=" Bigger" align="middle" /><b> Bigger</b></a>
